OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine,
OL,6,Fsunny evening for many, but cloudier
OL,7,Fand perhaps misty for many coastal
OL,8,Fparts. Cloud spreading inland
OL,9,Fovernight, but remaining largely dry
OL,10,Fwith a light northeasterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEarly cloud retreating to
OL,13,Fthe coast through the morning. Plenty
OL,14,Fof sunshine follows, and feeling very
OL,15,Fwarm, especially in the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
