OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FGenerally cloudy mornings with sunny
OL,7,Fspells developing by the afternoons.
OL,8,FRemaining largely dry throughout.
OL,9,FBreezy at times, especially along the
OL,10,Fcoast. Feeling warm by day with
OL,11,Ftemperatures remaining above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
